# Tier4 Release Train Conductor

CLOSURE_CREATE FRACTAL_METASCRIPT "Tier4ReleaseTrain"
  grammar="@metascripts/fragments/safety_rules.trsx"
  context.squad="ReleaseTrain"
  context.role="DeliveryLead"
  context.stage="Tier4"

NOTE "Bundle validated Tier3/Tier4 artifacts with provenance and schedule promotion experiments."

METRIC promotion_success 0.95
METRIC provenance_completeness 1.00

SPAWN DeliveryAgent 1 HIERARCHICAL
SPAWN ProvenanceScribe 1 FRACTAL
SPAWN RiskOfficer 1 DEMOCRATIC
CONNECT DeliveryAgent ProvenanceScribe package
CONNECT ProvenanceScribe RiskOfficer audit
REPEAT release-window 3
